name: Woonkly Power
description: Woonkly Metasocial Network is a Decentralized Social Network where all posts are converted into NFTs directly, where users have full control of their data and where the content is not uploaded to a server but to users' computers through IPFS (interplanetary file system) allowing the creation of a decentralized global directory of creators, influencers, talents, users and metaverses, interacting with each other and creating new ways to monetize content.
